        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Stocky Swap by Stack Architect is the direct free replacement for Stocky. It replicates Stocky's core features — purchase orders, supplier management, and demand forecasting — and is permanently free with no subscription required. Other paid alternatives include Brightpearl, Linnworks, and Inventory Planner."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "When is Shopify shutting down Stocky?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Shopify is shutting down the Stocky inventory management app in August 2026. After this date, Stocky will no longer be available and merchants need to migrate to an alternative before the shutdown."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Stocky Swap really free?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. Stocky Swap is permanently free — no subscription, no trial period, no hidden fees. It is built and maintained by Stack Architect as a free tool for Shopify merchants affected by the Stocky shutdown."
