      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Stocky's core features are: purchase orders, supplier management, inventory demand forecasting, suggested orders based on sales velocity, and stock transfer between locations. Stocky Swap covers all of these features. More advanced warehouse management and multi-channel sync require a paid tool like Brightpearl or Linnworks."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to migrate from Stocky?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Most merchants can migrate from Stocky to Stocky Swap in under 30 minutes. The migration involves exporting supplier data from Stocky, importing it into Stocky Swap, and verifying your purchase order history. A step-by-step migration guide is available on the Stocky Swap page."
