        Shopify is shutting down Stocky in August 2026. The exact date has not been confirmed but merchants should plan to migrate before the end of July 2026 to ensure continuity. Export your Stocky data — purchase orders, supplier contacts, and inventory history — as early as possible to avoid losing it.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
