        Yes. Stocky Swap works with all Shopify plans including Basic, Shopify, Advanced, and Plus. It connects to your Shopify store's products, variants, and inventory through the standard Shopify API and does not require any specific plan tier.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        What happens to my Stocky data when it shuts down?
        <span class="chevron">▾</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        When Stocky shuts down, your purchase order history, supplier data, and demand forecasting settings stored within the app will become inaccessible. Before August 2026, export all data from Stocky: go to Reports → Export in your Stocky dashboard to download CSV files of your purchase orders and supplier contacts. Import these into Stocky Swap or whichever replacement you choose.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        Is there a Shopify-native inventory replacement coming?
